t. The discovery of this new invariant is analogous to that of\nthe order structure on the total K-theory when one advances from the\nclassification of simple real rank zero $C^*$-algebras to that of non simple\nreal rank zero $C^*$-algebras in [G2], [Ei], [DL] and [DG] (see Introduction\nbelow).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2016 08:14:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 May 2019 14:42:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-29"}
