 1000$ hrs) by SKA1-low in\nthe frequency range $\\nu \\simgt 75-90$ MHz, for clusters in the temperature\nrange 5 to 20 keV, and the difference between the SZE-21cm and the standard SZE\ncan be detected by SKA1 or SKA2 at frequencies depending on the background\nmodel and the cluster temperature. [abridged]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2016 14:32:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-26"}
